{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852713496,"sessionID":"ses_286ee9b3dffesjGz3k6Rl1TiT0","part":{"id":"prt_d7911f202001VqKVS4x1SqKGzX","messageID":"msg_d7911e475001zmNK9ZBakDk3c8","sessionID":"ses_286ee9b3dffesjGz3k6Rl1TiT0","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_3215b4ace47e45079631a361","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/router/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/router/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发\n2: \n3: - **AR ID**: AR-011\n4: - **Module**: `pkg/router`\n5: - **Language**: Go\n6: - **Size**: M\n7: - **Status**: Draft\n8: - **Base**: AR-010 (Session Management)\n9: \n10: ## 1. 概述\n11: \n12: 本设计文档聚焦于 **JWT 认证与签发** 功能，为 `pkg/router` 模块增加基于 JWT 的身份验证和令牌管理能力。该功能是 AR-010 会话管理的扩展，提供安全的 API 访问控制。\n13: \n14: ### 1.1 目标\n15: \n16: - 实现 JWT Token 验证（支持 HS256、RS256 算法）\n17: - 实现 JWT Token 签发（登录接口）\n18: - 实现 Token 刷新接口\n19: - 支持可配置的 JWT 参数（Issuer、Audience、Expiry）\n20: - 提供 JWT 指标监控\n21: \n22: ### 1.2 依赖\n23: \n24: - `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` — JWT 令牌处理\n25: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/router` — 现有路由模块\n26: \n27: ---\n28: \n29: ## 2. 架构设计\n30: \n31: ### 2.1 整体架构\n32: \n33: ```\n34: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n35: │                         Router Server (pkg/router)                       │\n36: │  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐    │\n37: │  │   JWT       │→ │  Auth       │→ │  Rate Limit │→ │   Proxy     │    │\n38: │  │ Middleware  │  │ Middleware  │  │  Middleware  │  │   Handler   │    │\n39: │  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘    │\n40: │         │                                                                    │\n41: │  ┌──────▼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐         │\n42: │  │                    JWT Manager                               │         │\n43: │  │  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐         │         │\n44: │  │  │   Token     │  │   Token     │  │   Key       │         │         │\n45: │  │  │  Validation│  │  Issuance   │  │  Management │         │         │\n46: │  │  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘         │         │\n47: │  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘         │\n48: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n49: ```\n50: \n51: ### 2.2 组件职责\n52: \n53: | 组件 | 职责 |\n54: |------|------|\n55: | `JWTMiddleware` | 拦截请求，提取并验证 JWT Token |\n56: | `JWTManager` | 核心 JWT 操作：签发、验证、刷新 |\n57: | `KeyManager` | 密钥管理（HS256 对称密钥、RS256 非对称密钥） |\n58: | `LoginHandler` | 处理用户登录，签发 Token |\n59: | `RefreshHandler` | 处理 Token 刷新 |\n60: \n61: ### 2.3 数据流\n62: \n63: ```\n64: 1. 客户端请求进入 Router\n65:    │\n66: 2. JWTMiddleware 检查公开端点\n67:    ├── 公开端点 → 跳过验证，继续处理\n68:    │\n69: 3. JWTMiddleware 提取 Token\n70:    ├── 从 Header: Authorization: Bearer <token>\n71:    ├── 或从 Query: ?token=<token>\n72:    │\n73: 4. JWTManager 验证 Token\n74:    ├── 检查签名\n75:    ├── 检查过期时间\n76:    ├── 检查 Issuer\n77:    ├── 检查 Audience\n78:    │\n79: 5. 验证通过 → 将 Claims 写入 Context → 传递给下游 Handler\n80:    │\n81: 6. 验证失败 → 返回 401 Unauthorized\n82: ```\n83: \n84: ---\n85: \n86: ## 3. 数据结构\n87: \n88: ### 3.1 JWT 配置\n89: \n90: ```go\n91: // JWTConfig holds JWT-specific configuration\n92: type JWTConfig struct {\n93:     Enabled         bool          // Enable JWT authentication (default: false)\n94:     Algorithm       string        // Algorithm: \"HS256\" or \"RS256\" (default: \"HS256\")\n95:     Secret          string        // Secret key for HS256\n96:     PrivateKeyPath  string        // Path to RSA private key for RS256\n97:     PublicKeyPath   string        // Path to RSA public key for RS256\n98:     Issuer          string        // Token issuer (default: \"agentcube\")\n99:     Audience        []string      // Expected audience claims\n100:     Expiration      time.Duration // Token expiration (default: 1h)\n101:     RefreshExpiration time.Duration // Refresh token expiration (default: 24h)\n102:     ClockSkew       time.Duration // Clock skew tolerance (default: 30s)\n103:     AllowQueryParam bool          // Allow token in query parameter (default: false)\n104: }\n105: ```\n106: \n107: ### 3.2 JWT 声明\n108: \n109: ```go\n110: // Claims represents standard JWT claims\n111: type Claims struct {\n112:     jwt.RegisteredClaims\n113:     // Custom claims\n114:     Roles     []string          `json:\"roles,omitempty\"`\n115:     TenantID  string            `json:\"tenant_id,omitempty\"`\n116:     Namespace string            `json:\"namespace,omitempty\"`\n117: }\n118: \n119: // UserCredentials represents login request\n120: type UserCredentials struct {\n121:     Username string `json:\"username\" binding:\"required\"`\n122:     Password string `json:\"password\" binding:\"required\"`\n123: }\n124: \n125: // LoginResponse represents login response\n126: type LoginResponse struct {\n127:     AccessToken  string `json:\"access_token\"`\n128:     RefreshToken string `json:\"refresh_token\"`\n129:     TokenType    string `json:\"token_type\"`\n130:     ExpiresIn    int64  `json:\"expires_in\"`\n131: }\n132: \n133: // TokenRefreshRequest represents refresh token request\n134: type TokenRefreshRequest struct {\n135:     RefreshToken string `json:\"refresh_token\" binding:\"required\"`\n136: }\n137: ```\n138: \n139: ### 3.3 JWT 管理器\n140: \n141: ```go\n142: // JWTManager handles JWT token operations\n143: type JWTManager struct {\n144:     config          *JWTConfig\n145:     secretKey       []byte\n146:     privateKey      *rsa.PrivateKey\n147:     publicKey       *rsa.PublicKey\n148:     metrics         *JWTMetrics\n149:     userValidator   UserValidator\n150:     mu              sync.RWMutex\n151: }\n152: \n153: // UserValidator validates user credentials\n154: type UserValidator interface {\n155:     Validate(username, password string) (*UserClaims, error)\n156: }\n157: \n158: // UserClaims represents authenticated user info\n159: type UserClaims struct {\n160:     Username  string\n161:     Roles     []string\n162:     TenantID  string\n163:     Namespace string\n164: }\n165: ```\n166: \n167: ### 3.4 更新配置结构\n168: \n169: ```go\n170: // Config (extended from AR-010)\n171: type Config struct {\n172:     // ... existing fields ...\n173:     \n174:     // JWT settings\n175:     JWT JWTConfig // JWT configuration\n176: }\n177: \n178: // DefaultConfig returns config with JWT defaults\n179: func DefaultConfig() *Config {\n180:     return &Config{\n181:         // ... existing defaults ...\n182:         JWT: JWTConfig{\n183:             Enabled:         false,\n184:             Algorithm:       \"HS256\",\n185:             Secret:          \"\",\n186:             Issuer:          \"agentcube\",\n187:             Audience:        nil,\n188:             Expiration:      1 * time.Hour,\n189:             RefreshExpiration: 24 * time.Hour,\n190:             ClockSkew:       30 * time.Second,\n191:             AllowQueryParam: false,\n192:         },\n193:     }\n194: }\n195: ```\n196: \n197: ---\n198: \n199: ## 4. API 合约\n200: \n201: ### 4.1 新增端点\n202: \n203: | Method | Path | Middleware | Handler | Description |\n204: |--------|------|------------|---------|-------------|\n205: | POST | `/login` | none | `handleLogin` | 用户登录，签发 Token |\n206: | POST | `/refresh` | none | `handleRefresh` | 刷新 Token |\n207: | GET | `/validate` | JWT | `handleValidate` | 验证当前 Token |\n208: \n209: ### 4.2 受保护端点（需 JWT）\n210: \n211: | Method | Path | Description |\n212: |--------|------|-------------|\n213: | GET | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/*path` | AgentRuntime 代理 |\n214: | POST | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/*path` | AgentRuntime 代理 |\n215: | GET | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/*path` | CodeInterpreter 代理 |\n216: | POST | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/*path` | CodeInterpreter 代理 |\n217: \n218: ### 4.3 公开端点（跳过 JWT）\n219: \n220: - `/health/live`\n221: - `/health/ready`\n222: - `/metrics`\n223: - `/login`\n224: - `/refresh`\n225: \n226: ### 4.4 登录请求/响应\n227: \n228: ```json\n229: // POST /login - Request\n230: {\n231:     \"username\": \"admin\",\n232:     \"password\": \"secret\"\n233: }\n234: \n235: // Response - Success\n236: {\n237:     \"access_token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n238:     \"refresh_token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n239:     \"token_type\": \"Bearer\",\n240:     \"expires_in\": 3600\n241: }\n242: \n243: // Response - Error\n244: {\n245:     \"error\": \"invalid credentials\",\n246:     \"code\": \"ERR_INVALID_CREDENTIALS\",\n247:     \"requestId\": \"req-xxx\"\n248: }\n249: ```\n250: \n251: ### 4.5 Token 刷新请求/响应\n252: \n253: ```json\n254: // POST /refresh - Request\n255: {\n256:     \"refresh_token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\"\n257: }\n258: \n259: // Response - Success\n260: {\n261:     \"access_token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...\",\n262:     \"token_type\": \"Bearer\",\n263:     \"expires_in\": 3600\n264: }\n265: ```\n266: \n267: ### 4.6 错误响应\n268: \n269: | Status Code | Description | Error Code |\n270: |-------------|-------------|------------|\n271: | 200 | Success | - |\n272: | 400 | Bad Request (malformed token) | `ERR_MALFORMED_TOKEN` |\n273: | 401 | Unauthorized (invalid/expired token) | `ERR_UNAUTHORIZED` |\n274: | 401 | Invalid credentials | `ERR_INVALID_CREDENTIALS` |\n275: | 401 | Invalid audience | `ERR_INVALID_AUDIENCE` |\n276: | 401 | Invalid issuer | `ERR_INVALID_ISSUER` |\n277: | 401 | Invalid signature | `ERR_INVALID_SIGNATURE` |\n278: | 401 | Token expired | `ERR_TOKEN_EXPIRED` |\n279: | 401 | Invalid refresh token | `ERR_INVALID_REFRESH_TOKEN` |\n280: \n281: ---\n282: \n283: ## 5. 实现细节\n284: \n285: ### 5.1 JWT 验证流程\n286: \n287: ```go\n288: func (m *JWTManager) ValidateToken(tokenString string) (*Claims, error) {\n289:     // Parse token without validation first\n290:     token, _, err := jwt.NewParser().ParseUnverified(tokenString, &Claims{})\n291:     if err != nil {\n292:         return nil, fmt.Errorf(\"%w: %v\", ErrMalformedToken, err)\n293:     }\n294:     \n295:     // Select validation key based on algorithm\n296:     var validationKey interface{}\n297:     switch m.config.Algorithm {\n298:     case \"HS256\":\n299:         validationKey = m.secretKey\n300:     case \"RS256\":\n301:         validationKey = m.publicKey\n302:     }\n303:     \n304:     // Validate token\n305:     claims := &Claims{}\n306:     token, err = jwt.ParseWithClaims(tokenString, claims, func(token *jwt.Token) (interface{}, error) {\n307:         // Verify signing method\n308:         switch m.config.Algorithm {\n309:         case \"HS256\":\n310:             _, ok := token.Method.(*jwt.SigningMethodHMAC)\n311:             if !ok {\n312:                 return nil, fmt.Errorf(\"%w: unexpected signing method: %v\", ErrInvalidSignature, token.Header[\"alg\"])\n313:             }\n314:         case \"RS256\":\n315:             _, ok := token.Method.(*jwt.SigningMethodRSA)\n316:             if !ok {\n317:                 return nil, fmt.Errorf(\"%w: unexpected signing method: %v\", ErrInvalidSignature, token.Header[\"alg\"])\n318:             }\n319:         }\n320:         return validationKey, nil\n321:     }, jwt.WithIssuer(m.config.Issuer),\n322:        jwt.WithAudience(m.config.Audience...),\n323:        jwt.WithClockSkew(m.config.ClockSkew))\n324:     \n325:     if err != nil {\n326:         if errors.Is(err, jwt.ErrTokenExpired) {\n327:             return nil, ErrTokenExpired\n328:         }\n329:         if errors.Is(err, jwt.ErrTokenSignatureInvalid) {\n330:             return nil, ErrInvalidSignature\n331:         }\n332:         return nil, fmt.Errorf(\"%w: %v\", ErrUnauthorized, err)\n333:     }\n334:     \n335:     return claims, nil\n336: }\n337: ```\n338: \n339: ### 5.2 JWT 签发流程\n340: \n341: ```go\n342: func (m *JWTManager) IssueToken(user *UserClaims) (string, error) {\n343:     now := time.Now()\n344:     \n345:     claims := Claims{\n346:         RegisteredClaims: jwt.RegisteredClaims{\n347:             ExpiresAt: jwt.NewNumericDate(now.Add(m.config.Expiration)),\n348:             IssuedAt:  jwt.NewNumericDate(now),\n349:             NotBefore: jwt.NewNumericDate(now),\n350:             Issuer:    m.config.Issuer,\n351:             ID:        uuid.New().String(),\n352:         },\n353:         Roles:     user.Roles,\n354:         TenantID:  user.TenantID,\n355:         Namespace: user.Namespace,\n356:     }\n357:     \n358:     // Add audience if configured\n359:     if len(m.config.Audience) > 0 {\n360:         claims.Audience = m.config.Audience\n361:     }\n362:     \n363:     // Sign token based on algorithm\n364:     var tokenString string\n365:     var err error\n366:     \n367:     switch m.config.Algorithm {\n368:     case \"HS256\":\n369:         tokenString, err = jwt.NewWithClaims(jwt.SigningMethodHS256, claims).SignedString(m.secretKey)\n370:     case \"RS256\":\n371:         tokenString, err = jwt.NewWithClaims(jwt.SigningMethodRS256, claims).SignedString(m.privateKey)\n372:     default:\n373:         return \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"unsupported algorithm: %s\", m.config.Algorithm)\n374:     }\n375:     \n376:     if err != nil {\n377:         return \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"failed to sign token: %w\", err)\n378:     }\n379:     \n380:     m.metrics.IssuedTotal.Inc()\n381:     return tokenString, nil\n382: }\n383: ```\n384: \n385: ### 5.3 中间件实现\n386: \n387: ```go\n388: // JWTMiddleware creates JWT authentication middleware\n389: func JWTMiddleware(manager *JWTManager, publicPaths []string) Middleware {\n390:     publicPathSet := make(map[string]bool)\n391:     for _, path := range publicPaths {\n392:         publicPathSet[path] = true\n393:     }\n394:     \n395:     return func(next http.Handler) http.Handler {\n396:         return http.HandlerFunc(func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n397:             // Check if public path\n398:             if publicPathSet[r.URL.Path] {\n399:                 next.ServeHTTP(w, r)\n400:                 return\n401:             }\n402:             \n403:             // Extract token\n404:             tokenString, err := extractToken(r, manager.config.AllowQueryParam)\n405:             if err != nil {\n406:                 http.Error(w, err.Error(), http.StatusBadRequest)\n407:                 return\n408:             }\n409:             \n410:             // Validate token\n411:             claims, err := manager.ValidateToken(tokenString)\n412:             if err != nil {\n413:                 manager.metrics.ValidationErrorsTotal.WithLabelValues(getErrorType(err)).Inc()\n414:                 http.Error(w, \"Unauthorized\", http.StatusUnauthorized)\n415:                 return\n416:             }\n417:             \n418:             // Add claims to context\n419:             ctx := context.WithValue(r.Context(), ContextKeyClaims, claims)\n420:             ctx = context.WithValue(ctx, ContextKeyUsername, claims.Subject)\n421:             \n422:             manager.metrics.ValidatedTotal.WithLabelValues(\"success\").Inc()\n423:             next.ServeHTTP(w, r.WithContext(ctx))\n424:         })\n425:     }\n426: }\n427: \n428: func extractToken(r *http.Request, allowQueryParam bool) (string, error) {\n429:     // Try Authorization header first\n430:     authHeader := r.Header.Get(\"Authorization\")\n431:     if authHeader != \"\" {\n432:         parts := strings.SplitN(authHeader, \" \", 2)\n433:         if len(parts) == 2 && strings.ToLower(parts[0]) == \"bearer\" {\n434:             return parts[1], nil\n435:         }\n436:     }\n437:     \n438:     // Try query parameter if allowed\n439:     if allowQueryParam {\n440:         if token := r.URL.Query().Get(\"token\"); token != \"\" {\n441:             return token, nil\n442:         }\n443:     }\n444:     \n445:     return \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"%w: no token found\", ErrMalformedToken)\n446: }\n447: ```\n448: \n449: ### 5.4 登录处理器\n450: \n451: ```go\n452: func (m *JWTManager) HandleLogin(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n453:     var creds UserCredentials\n454:     if err := json.NewDecoder(r.Body).Decode(&creds); err != nil {\n455:         writeError(w, \"bad request\", \"ERR_BAD_REQUEST\", http.StatusBadRequest)\n456:         return\n457:     }\n458:     \n459:     // Validate credentials\n460:     user, err := m.userValidator.Validate(creds.Username, creds.Password)\n461:     if err != nil {\n462:         writeError(w, \"invalid credentials\", \"ERR_INVALID_CREDENTIALS\", http.StatusUnauthorized)\n463:         return\n464:     }\n465:     \n466:     // Issue tokens\n467:     accessToken, err := m.IssueToken(user)\n468:     if err != nil {\n469:         writeError(w, \"failed to issue token\", \"ERR_TOKEN_ISSUANCE_FAILED\", http.StatusInternalServerError)\n470:         return\n471:     }\n472:     \n473:     refreshToken, err := m.IssueRefreshToken(user)\n474:     if err != nil {\n475:         writeError(w, \"failed to issue refresh token\", \"ERR_TOKEN_ISSUANCE_FAILED\", http.StatusInternalServerError)\n476:         return\n477:     }\n478:     \n479:     response := LoginResponse{\n480:         AccessToken:  accessToken,\n481:         RefreshToken: refreshToken,\n482:         TokenType:    \"Bearer\",\n483:         ExpiresIn:    int64(m.config.Expiration.Seconds()),\n484:     }\n485:     \n486:     w.Header().Set(\"Content-Type\", \"application/json\")\n487:     json.NewEncoder(w).Encode(response)\n488: }\n489: ```\n490: \n491: ### 5.5 密钥管理\n492: \n493: ```go\n494: // KeyManager handles JWT key loading and management\n495: type KeyManager struct {\n496:     config *JWTConfig\n497: }\n498: \n499: func (km *KeyManager) LoadKeys() error {\n500:     switch km.config.Algorithm {\n501:     case \"HS256\":\n502:         if km.config.Secret == \"\" {\n503:             return fmt.Errorf(\"JWT secret is required for HS256\")\n504:         }\n505:         km.config.Secret = os.Getenv(\"JWT_SECRET\") // Override from env if set\n506:     case \"RS256\":\n507:         if km.config.PrivateKeyPath == \"\" || km.config.PublicKeyPath == \"\" {\n508:             return fmt.Errorf(\"JWT key paths are required for RS256\")\n509:         }\n510:         \n511:         privateKeyData, err := os.ReadFile(km.config.PrivateKeyPath)\n512:         if err != nil {\n513:             return fmt.Errorf(\"failed to read private key: %w\", err)\n514:         }\n515:         \n516:         privateKey, err := jwt.ParseRSAPrivateKeyFromPEM(privateKeyData)\n517:         if err != nil {\n518:             return fmt.Errorf(\"failed to parse private key: %w\", err)\n519:         }\n520:         \n521:         publicKeyData, err := os.ReadFile(km.config.PublicKeyPath)\n522:         if err != nil {\n523:             return fmt.Errorf(\"failed to read public key: %w\", err)\n524:         }\n525:         \n526:         publicKey, err := jwt.ParseRSAPublicKeyFromPEM(publicKeyData)\n527:         if err != nil {\n528:             return fmt.Errorf(\"failed to parse public key: %w\", err)\n529:         }\n530:     }\n531:     \n532:     return nil\n533: }\n534: ```\n535: \n536: ---\n537: \n538: ## 6. 错误处理\n539: \n540: ### 6.1 错误类型\n541: \n542: ```go\n543: // JWT Errors\n544: var (\n545:     ErrMalformedToken     = errors.New(\"malformed token\")\n546:     ErrInvalidSignature   = errors.New(\"invalid signature\")\n547:     ErrTokenExpired       = errors.New(\"token expired\")\n548:     ErrInvalidAudience    = errors.New(\"invalid audience\")\n549:     ErrInvalidIssuer      = errors.New(\"invalid issuer\")\n550:     ErrUnauthorized       = errors.New(\"unauthorized\")\n551:     ErrInvalidCredentials = errors.New(\"invalid credentials\")\n552:     ErrInvalidRefreshToken = errors.New(\"invalid refresh token\")\n553: )\n554: \n555: // Error codes\n556: const (\n557:     ErrCodeMalformedToken      = \"ERR_MALFORMED_TOKEN\"\n558:     ErrCodeInvalidSignature   = \"ERR_INVALID_SIGNATURE\"\n559:     ErrCodeTokenExpired        = \"ERR_TOKEN_EXPIRED\"\n560:     ErrCodeInvalidAudience    = \"ERR_INVALID_AUDIENCE\"\n561:     ErrCodeInvalidIssuer       = \"ERR_INVALID_ISSUER\"\n562:     ErrCodeUnauthorized       = \"ERR_UNAUTHORIZED\"\n563:     ErrCodeInvalidCredentials  = \"ERR_INVALID_CREDENTIALS\"\n564:     ErrCodeInvalidRefreshToken = \"ERR_INVALID_REFRESH_TOKEN\"\n565: )\n566: ```\n567: \n568: ### 6.2 错误处理策略\n569: \n570: | 错误场景 | HTTP 状态码 | 处理策略 |\n571: |----------|-------------|----------|\n572: | Token 格式错误 | 400 | 记录错误，返回 \"malformed token\" |\n573: | Token 签名无效 | 401 | 记录错误指标，返回 \"invalid signature\" |\n574: | Token 已过期 | 401 | 记录错误指标，返回 \"token expired\" |\n575: | Audience 不匹配 | 401 | 记录错误指标，返回 \"invalid audience\" |\n576: | Issuer 不匹配 | 401 | 记录错误指标，返回 \"invalid issuer\" |\n577: | 无效凭证 | 401 | 记录错误指标，返回 \"invalid credentials\" |\n578: | 无效刷新 Token | 401 | 记录错误指标，返回 \"invalid refresh token\" |\n579: \n580: ---\n581: \n582: ## 7. 监控指标\n583: \n584: ### 7.1 Prometheus 指标\n585: \n586: | Metric | Type | Labels | Description |\n587: |--------|------|--------|-------------|\n588: | `jwt_validated_total` | Counter | result (success/error) | JWT validation count |\n589: | `jwt_issued_total` | Counter | - | JWT token issuance count |\n590: | `jwt_refreshed_total` | Counter | result | JWT token refresh count |\n591: | `jwt_validation_errors_total` | Counter | error_type | JWT validation errors |\n592: \n593: ### 7.2 指标实现\n594: \n595: ```go\n596: type JWTMetrics struct {\n597:     ValidatedTotal        *prometheus.CounterVec\n598:     IssuedTotal          prometheus.Counter\n599:     RefreshedTotal       *prometheus.CounterVec\n600:     ValidationErrorsTotal *prometheus.CounterVec\n601: }\n602: \n603: func NewJWTMetrics() *JWTMetrics {\n604:     return &JWTMetrics{\n605:         ValidatedTotal: prometheus.NewCounterVec(\n606:             prometheus.CounterOpts{\n607:                 Name: \"jwt_validated_total\",\n608:                 Help: \"Total number of JWT validations\",\n609:             },\n610:             []string{\"result\"},\n611:         ),\n612:         IssuedTotal: prometheus.NewCounter(\n613:             prometheus.CounterOpts{\n614:                 Name: \"jwt_issued_total\",\n615:                 Help: \"Total number of JWT tokens issued\",\n616:             },\n617:         ),\n618:         RefreshedTotal: prometheus.NewCounterVec(\n619:             prometheus.CounterOpts{\n620:                 Name: \"jwt_refreshed_total\",\n621:                 Help: \"Total number of JWT token refreshes\",\n622:             },\n623:             []string{\"result\"},\n624:         ),\n625:         ValidationErrorsTotal: prometheus.NewCounterVec(\n626:             prometheus.CounterOpts{\n627:                 Name: \"jwt_validation_errors_total\",\n628:                 Help: \"Total number of JWT validation errors\",\n629:             },\n630:             []string{\"error_type\"},\n631:         ),\n632:     }\n633: }\n634: ```\n635: \n636: ---\n637: \n638: ## 8. 测试策略\n639: \n640: ### 8.1 单元测试\n641: \n642: | 模块 | 测试重点 |\n643: |------|----------|\n644: | `JWTManager` | Token 签发、验证、刷新、算法切换 |\n645: | `KeyManager` | 密钥加载、HS256/RS256 切换 |\n646: | `JWTMiddleware` | Token 提取、公开端点跳过、Context 传递 |\n647: | `LoginHandler` | 登录成功、失败、错误处理 |\n648: | `RefreshHandler` | 刷新成功、过期 Token 拒绝 |\n649: \n650: ### 8.2 测试场景\n651: \n652: | 场景 | 预期结果 |\n653: |------|----------|\n654: | 有效 JWT Token 验证 | 验证成功，Claims 正确解析 |\n655: | 过期 JWT Token 验证 | 返回 ErrTokenExpired |\n656: | 无效签名 JWT | 返回 ErrInvalidSignature |\n657: | 错误 Audience | 返回 ErrInvalidAudience |\n658: | 登录成功 | 返回 AccessToken 和 RefreshToken |\n659: | 登录失败（错误密码） | 返回 401 |\n660: | Token 刷新成功 | 返回新的 AccessToken |\n661: | Token 刷新（过期 RefreshToken） | 返回 401 |\n662: \n663: ### 8.3 测试覆盖率目标\n664: \n665: | 组件 | 目标覆盖率 |\n666: |------|-----------|\n667: | auth.go | 90% |\n668: | jwt.go (new) | 90% |\n669: \n670: ---\n671: \n672: ## 9. 实施计划\n673: \n674: ### Phase 1: 核心功能\n675: - [ ] 定义 JWTConfig 配置结构\n676: - [ ] 实现 JWTManager 核心逻辑\n677: - [ ] 实现 Token 签发和验证\n678: \n679: ### Phase 2: API 端点\n680: - [ ] 实现 /login 端点\n681: - [ ] 实现 /refresh 端点\n682: \n683: ### Phase 3: 中间件\n684: - [ ] 实现 JWT 中间件\n685: - [ ] 配置公开端点列表\n686: - [ ] 实现 Claims 传递到 Context\n687: \n688: ### Phase 4: 密钥管理\n689: - [ ] 实现 HS256 对称密钥支持\n690: - [ ] 实现 RS256 非对称密钥支持\n691: \n692: ### Phase 5: 监控和测试\n693: - [ ] 添加 Prometheus 指标\n694: - [ ] 编写单元测试\n695: - [ ] 集成测试\n696: \n697: ---\n698: \n699: ## 10. 依赖\n700: \n701: ### 10.1 外部依赖\n702: \n703: | Package | Version | Purpose |\n704: |---------|---------|---------|\n705: | `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` | ^5.0.0 | JWT token handling |\n706: | `github.com/prometheus/client_golang/prometheus` | ^1.16.0 | Metrics |\n707: \n708: ### 10.2 内部依赖\n709: \n710: | Module | Purpose |\n711: |--------|---------|\n712: | `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/router` | Existing router module |\n713: \n714: ---\n715: \n716: ## 11. 参考\n717: \n718: - [Delta Spec: AR-011](changes/AR-011/delta-spec.md)\n719: - [Proposal](proposal.md)\n720: - [AR-010: Router Session Management](pkg/router/design.md)\n721: - [JWT RFC 7519](https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7519)\n722: - [golang-jwt library](https://github.com/golang-jwt/jwt)\n\n(End of file - total 722 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-011 — Router JWT 认证与签发\n\n- **AR ID**: AR-011\n- **Module**: `pkg/router`\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: M\n- **Status**: Draft\n- **Base**: AR-010 (Session Management)\n\n## 1. 概述\n\n本设计文档聚焦于 **JWT 认证与签发** 功能，为 `pkg/router` 模块增加基于 JWT 的身份验证和令牌管理能力。该功能是 AR-010 会话管理的扩展，提供安全的 API 访问控制。\n\n### 1.1 目标\n\n- 实现 JWT Token 验证（支持 HS256、RS256 算法）\n- 实现 JWT Token 签发（登录接口）\n- 实现 Token 刷新接口\n- 支持可配置的 JWT 参数（Issuer、Audience、Expiry）\n- 提供 JWT 指标监控","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/router/design.md","time":{"start":1775852713485,"end":1775852713492}}}}
