{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775852808631,"sessionID":"ses_286ee9b3dffesjGz3k6Rl1TiT0","part":{"id":"prt_d791240ae001qssIe9Qq5qoxt3","messageID":"msg_d791233fe001pWhMeeg7fksvBH","sessionID":"ses_286ee9b3dffesjGz3k6Rl1TiT0","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_88731f50fcc642f8a1ffa38c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-015 — PicoD 命令执行 API\n\n- **AR ID**: AR-015\n- **Module**: `pkg/picod`\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: M\n- **Status**: ST-1 Completed (design.md)\n- **Previous Stage**: AR-015 ST-1 completed\n\n## 1. 概述\n\n本设计文档描述 PicoD 命令执行 API 的技术实现细节。PicoD 是一个基于 HTTP 的命令行执行服务，提供安全的命令执行、文件上传下载功能，支持 JWT 认证和 Workspace 目录隔离。\n\n### 1.1 目标\n\n- 实现安全的命令行执行 API\n- 提供文件上传、下载、列表功能\n- 基于 JWT 的请求认证\n- Workspace 目录隔离和路径安全检查\n\n### 1.2 依赖\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|---------|\n| `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` | ^1.9.x | HTTP 框架 |\n| `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` | ^5.0.0 | JWT 验证 |\n| `k8s.io/klog/v2` | ^2.x | 日志 |\n\n---\n\n## 2. 架构设计\n\n### 2.1 整体架构\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                           PicoD Server                                   │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\n│  │                     Gin HTTP Engine                                 │ │\n│  │  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌──────────┐ │ │\n│  │  │   Auth      │  │   Execute   │  │   Files     │  │  Health  │ │ │\n│  │  │  Middleware │  │   Handler   │  │   Handler   │  │  Check   │ │ │\n│  │  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘  └──────────┘ │ │\n│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\n│                                    │                                      │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\n│  │                    AuthManager                                        │ │\n│  │  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐                                    │ │\n│  │  │  Public Key │  │   JWT       │                                    │ │\n│  │  │  Loading    │  │  Validation │                                    │ │\n│  │  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘                                    │ │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\n│                                    │                                      │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐ │\n│  │                   Workspace Manager                                  │ │\n│  │  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐                                    │ │\n│  │  │   Path      │  │    File     │                                    │ │\n│  │  │  Sanitize   │  │   Operations│                                    │ │\n│  │  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘                                    │ │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### 2.2 组件职责\n\n| 组件 | 职责 |\n|------|------|\n| `Server` | HTTP 服务主入口，管理 Gin 引擎和配置 |\n| `AuthManager` | JWT 认证公钥加载和 Token 验证 |\n| `ExecuteHandler` | 处理命令执行请求，返回 stdout/stderr/exit code |\n| `UploadFileHandler` | 处理文件上传（JSON Base64 或 Multipart） |\n| `ListFilesHandler` | 列出目录文件 |\n| `DownloadFileHandler` | 文件下载 |\n| `HealthCheckHandler` | 健康检查接口 |\n| `sanitizePath` | 路径安全检查，防止目录穿越 |\n\n### 2.3 数据流\n\n```\n1. 客户端请求 → HTTP Server\n   │\n2. Auth Middleware 验证 JWT\n   ├── Token 有效 → 继续处理\n   ├── Token 无效 → 401 Unauthorized\n   │\n3. 请求路由到具体 Handler\n   ├── /api/execute → ExecuteHandler\n   ├── /api/files (POST) → UploadFileHandler\n   ├── /api/files (GET) → ListFilesHandler\n   ├── /api/files/*path → DownloadFileHandler\n   │\n4. Workspace 路径验证 (sanitizePath)\n   ├── 路径安全 → 执行操作\n   ├── 路径不安全 → 403 Forbidden\n   │\n5. 返回响应\n```\n\n---\n\n## 3. 数据结构\n\n### 3.1 配置结构\n\n```go\ntype Config struct {\n    Port      int    `json:\"port\"`\n    Workspace string `json:\"workspace\"`\n}\n```\n\n### 3.2 Server 结构\n\n```go\ntype Server struct {\n    engine       *gin.Engine\n    config       Config\n    authManager  *AuthManager\n    startTime    time.Time\n    workspaceDir string\n}\n```\n\n### 3.3 认证管理器\n\n```go\ntype AuthManager struct {\n    publicKey *rsa.PublicKey\n    mutex     sync.RWMutex\n}\n```\n\n### 3.4 请求/响应结构\n\n#### Execute\n\n```go\ntype ExecuteRequest struct {\n    Command    []string          `json:\"command\" binding:\"required\"`\n    Timeout    string            `json:\"timeout\"`\n    WorkingDir string            `json:\"working_dir\"`\n    Env        map[string]string `json:\"env\"`\n}\n\ntype ExecuteResponse struct {\n    Stdout    string    `json:\"stdout\"`\n    Stderr    string    `json:\"stderr\"`\n    ExitCode  int       `json:\"exit_code\"`\n    Duration  float64   `json:\"duration\"`\n    StartTime time.Time `json:\"start_time\"`\n    EndTime   time.Time `json:\"end_time\"`\n}\n```\n\n#### Files\n\n```go\ntype FileInfo struct {\n    Path     string    `json:\"path\"`\n    Size     int64     `json:\"size\"`\n    Mode     string    `json:\"mode\"`\n    Modified time.Time `json:\"modified\"`\n}\n\ntype UploadFileRequest struct {\n    Path    string `json:\"path\" binding:\"required\"`\n    Content string `json:\"content\" binding:\"required\"`\n    Mode    string `json:\"mode\"`\n}\n\ntype FileEntry struct {\n    Name     string    `json:\"name\"`\n    Size     int64     `json:\"size\"`\n    Modified time.Time `json:\"modified\"`\n    Mode     string    `json:\"mode\"`\n    IsDir    bool      `json:\"is_dir\"`\n}\n\ntype ListFilesResponse struct {\n    Files []FileEntry `json:\"files\"`\n}\n```\n\n### 3.5 常量\n\n| 常量 | 值 | 说明 |\n|------|-----|------|\n| `TimeoutExitCode` | `124` | 超时退出码 |\n| `MaxBodySize` | `32 << 20` (32 MiB) | HTTP 请求体大小限制 |\n| `PublicKeyEnvVar` | `\"PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY\"` | 公钥环境变量名 |\n| `maxFileMode` | `0777` | 最大文件权限 |\n\n---\n\n## 4. API 合约\n\n### 4.1 端点列表\n\n| Method | Path | Middleware | Handler | Description |\n|--------|------|------------|---------|-------------|\n| POST | `/api/execute` | JWT | `ExecuteHandler` | 执行命令 |\n| POST | `/api/files` | JWT | `UploadFileHandler` | 上传文件 |\n| GET | `/api/files` | JWT | `ListFilesHandler` | 列出文件 |\n| GET | `/api/files/*path` | JWT | `DownloadFileHandler` | 下载文件 |\n| GET | `/health` | none | `HealthCheckHandler` | 健康检查 |\n\n### 4.2 请求/响应格式\n\n#### Execute\n\n```json\n// POST /api/execute - Request\n{\n    \"command\": [\"ls\", \"-la\"],\n    \"timeout\": \"30s\",\n    \"working_dir\": \"/workspace\",\n    \"env\": {\"DEBUG\": \"true\"}\n}\n\n// Response - Success\n{\n    \"stdout\": \"total 4\\ndrwxr-xr-x  2 root root 4096 Apr 11 02:14 .\\n\",\n    \"stderr\": \"\",\n    \"exit_code\": 0,\n    \"duration\": 0.023,\n    \"start_time\": \"2024-04-11T02:14:00Z\",\n    \"end_time\": \"2024-04-11T02:14:00Z\"\n}\n\n// Response - Error (timeout)\n{\n    \"stdout\": \"\",\n    \"stderr\": \"context deadline exceeded\",\n    \"exit_code\": 124,\n    \"duration\": 60.0,\n    \"start_time\": \"2024-04-11T02:14:00Z\",\n    \"end_time\": \"2024-04-11T02:15:00Z\"\n}\n```\n\n#### Upload File\n\n```json\n// POST /api/files - JSON Request\n{\n    \"path\": \"test.txt\",\n    \"content\": \"SGVsbG8gV29ybGQ=\",  // Base64 encoded\n    \"mode\": \"0644\"\n}\n\n// POST /api/files - Multipart Request\n// Content-Type: multipart/form-data\n// Form fields: path, file, mode (optional)\n\n// Response - Success\n{\n    \"path\": \"test.txt\",\n    \"size\": 11,\n    \"mode\": \"0644\",\n    \"modified\": \"2024-04-11T02:14:00Z\"\n}\n```\n\n#### List Files\n\n```json\n// GET /api/files?path=/workspace\n\n// Response\n{\n    \"files\": [\n        {\"name\": \"test.txt\", \"size\": 11, \"modified\": \"2024-04-11T02:14:00Z\", \"mode\": \"0644\", \"is_dir\": false},\n        {\"name\": \"subdir\", \"size\": 0, \"modified\": \"2024-04-11T02:14:00Z\", \"mode\": \"0755\", \"is_dir\": true}\n    ]\n}\n```\n\n#### Health Check\n\n```json\n// GET /health\n\n// Response\n{\n    \"status\": \"ok\",\n    \"service\": \"PicoD\",\n    \"version\": \"0.0.1\",\n    \"uptime\": \"1h2m3s\"\n}\n```\n\n### 4.3 错误响应\n\n| Status Code | Error Code | Description |\n|-------------|------------|-------------|\n| 400 | 400 | Bad Request (malformed JSON, missing fields) |\n| 401 | 401 | Unauthorized (missing/invalid JWT) |\n| 403 | 403 | Forbidden (path outside workspace) |\n| 404 | 404 | Not Found (file/directory not found) |\n| 500 | 500 | Internal Server Error |\n\n```json\n// Generic error\n{\"error\": \"error message\", \"code\": 400}\n\n// Auth error\n{\"error\": \"Invalid token\", \"code\": 401, \"detail\": \"signature invalid\"}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 5. 实现细节\n\n### 5.1 服务启动流程\n\n```go\nfunc main() {\n    klog.InitFlags(nil)\n    flag.Parse()\n    \n    config := picod.Config{\n        Port:      *port,\n        Workspace: *workspace,\n    }\n    \n    server, err := picod.NewServer(config)\n    if err != nil {\n        klog.Fatalf(\"Failed to create server: %v\", err)\n    }\n    \n    if err := server.Run(); err != nil {\n        klog.Fatalf(\"Server error: %v\", err)\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 5.2 Server 初始化\n\n```go\nfunc NewServer(config Config) (*Server, error) {\n    gin.SetMode(gin.ReleaseMode)\n    engine := gin.New()\n    engine.Use(gin.Logger(), gin.Recovery())\n    \n    authManager := &AuthManager{}\n    if err := authManager.LoadPublicKeyFromEnv(); err != nil {\n        klog.Fatalf(\"Failed to load public key: %v\", err)\n    }\n    \n    s := &Server{\n        engine:  engine,\n        config:  config,\n        authManager: authManager,\n        startTime: time.Now(),\n    }\n    \n    if err := s.setWorkspace(config.Workspace); err != nil {\n        return nil, err\n    }\n    \n    s.setupRoutes()\n    return s, nil\n}\n```\n\n### 5.3 路由设置\n\n```go\nfunc (s *Server) setupRoutes() {\n    api := s.engine.Group(\"/api\")\n    api.Use(s.authManager.AuthMiddleware())\n    {\n        api.POST(\"/execute\", s.ExecuteHandler)\n        api.POST(\"/files\", s.UploadFileHandler)\n        api.GET(\"/files\", s.ListFilesHandler)\n        api.GET(\"/files/*path\", s.DownloadFileHandler)\n    }\n    s.engine.GET(\"/health\", s.HealthCheckHandler)\n}\n```\n\n### 5.4 JWT 认证中间件\n\n```go\nfunc (am *AuthManager) AuthMiddleware() gin.HandlerFunc {\n    return func(c *gin.Context) {\n        authHeader := c.GetHeader(\"Authorization\")\n        if authHeader == \"\" {\n            c.JSON(http.StatusUnauthorized, gin.H{\n                \"error\":  \"missing authorization header\",\n                \"code\":   401,\n                \"detail\": \"JWT required\",\n            })\n            c.Abort()\n            return\n        }\n        \n        parts := strings.Split(authHeader, \" \")\n        if len(parts) != 2 || parts[0] != \"Bearer\" {\n            c.JSON(http.StatusUnauthorized, gin.H{\n                \"error\":  \"invalid authorization header format\",\n                \"code\":   401,\n                \"detail\": \"Use Bearer <token>\",\n            })\n            c.Abort()\n            return\n        }\n        \n        tokenString := parts[1]\n        token, err := jwt.Parse(tokenString, func(token *jwt.Token) (interface{}, error) {\n            if _, ok := token.Method.(*jwt.SigningMethodRSA); !ok {\n                return nil, fmt.Errorf(\"unexpected signing method: %v\", token.Header[\"alg\"])\n            }\n            am.mu.RLock()\n            defer am.mu.RUnlock()\n            return am.publicKey, nil\n        }, jwt.WithExpirationRequired(), jwt.WithIssuedAt(), jwt.WithLeeway(time.Minute))\n        \n        if err != nil || !token.Valid {\n            c.JSON(http.StatusUnauthorized, gin.H{\n                \"error\":  \"Invalid token\",\n                \"code\":   401,\n                \"detail\": err.Error(),\n            })\n            c.Abort()\n            return\n        }\n        \n        c.Request.Body = http.MaxBytesReader(c.Writer, c.Request.Body, MaxBodySize)\n        c.Next()\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 5.5 公钥加载\n\n```go\nfunc (am *AuthManager) LoadPublicKeyFromEnv() error {\n    keyData := os.Getenv(PublicKeyEnvVar)\n    if keyData == \"\" {\n        return fmt.Errorf(\"environment variable %s is not set\", PublicKeyEnvVar)\n    }\n    \n    block, _ := pem.Decode([]byte(keyData))\n    if block == nil {\n        return fmt.Errorf(\"failed to decode PEM block\")\n    }\n    \n    pubKey, err := x509.ParsePKIXPublicKey(block.Bytes)\n    if err != nil {\n        return fmt.Errorf(\"failed to parse public key: %v\", err)\n    }\n    \n    rsaPubKey, ok := pubKey.(*rsa.PublicKey)\n    if !ok {\n        return fmt.Errorf(\"public key is not RSA\")\n    }\n    \n    am.mu.Lock()\n    defer am.mu.Unlock()\n    am.publicKey = rsaPubKey\n    \n    return nil\n}\n```\n\n### 5.6 命令执行 Handler\n\n```go\nfunc (s *Server) ExecuteHandler(c *gin.Context) {\n    var req ExecuteRequest\n    if err := c.ShouldBindJSON(&req); err != nil {\n        c.JSON(http.StatusBadRequest, gin.H{\"error\": err.Error(), \"code\": 400})\n        return\n    }\n    \n    timeout := 60 * time.Second\n    if req.Timeout != \"\" {\n        var err error\n        timeout, err = time.ParseDuration(req.Timeout)\n        if err != nil {\n            c.JSON(http.StatusBadRequest, gin.H{\"error\": \"invalid timeout format\", \"code\": 400})\n            return\n        }\n    }\n    \n    ctx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(c.Request.Context(), timeout)\n    defer cancel()\n    \n    workingDir := s.workspaceDir\n    if req.WorkingDir != \"\" {\n        safePath, err := s.sanitizePath(req.WorkingDir)\n        if err != nil {\n            c.JSON(http.StatusForbidden, gin.H{\"error\": err.Error(), \"code\": 403})\n            return\n        }\n        workingDir = safePath\n    }\n    \n    cmd := exec.CommandContext(ctx, req.Command[0], req.Command[1:]...)\n    cmd.Dir = workingDir\n    \n    if req.Env != nil {\n        env := os.Environ()\n        for k, v := range req.Env {\n            env = append(env, k+\"=\"+v)\n        }\n        cmd.Env = env\n    }\n    \n    var stdout, stderr bytes.Buffer\n    cmd.Stdout = &stdout\n    cmd.Stderr = &stderr\n    \n    startTime := time.Now()\n    err := cmd.Run()\n    endTime := time.Now()\n    duration := endTime.Sub(startTime).Seconds()\n    \n    exitCode := 0\n    if ctx.Err() == context.DeadlineExceeded {\n        exitCode = TimeoutExitCode\n        stderr.WriteString(\"context deadline exceeded\\n\")\n    } else if err != nil {\n        exitCode = 1\n        if stderr.Len() > 0 {\n            stderr.WriteString(\"\\n\")\n        }\n        stderr.WriteString(err.Error())\n    } else if cmd.ProcessState != nil {\n        exitCode = cmd.ProcessState.ExitCode()\n    }\n    \n    c.JSON(http.StatusOK, ExecuteResponse{\n        Stdout:    stdout.String(),\n        Stderr:    stderr.String(),\n        ExitCode:  exitCode,\n        Duration:  duration,\n        StartTime: startTime,\n        EndTime:   endTime,\n    })\n}\n```\n\n### 5.7 路径安全检查\n\n```go\nfunc (s *Server) sanitizePath(p string) (string, error) {\n    if s.workspaceDir == \"\" {\n        return \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"workspace directory not initialized\")\n    }\n    \n    resolvedWorkspace, err := filepath.EvalSymlinks(s.workspaceDir)\n    if err != nil {\n        resolvedWorkspace, _ = filepath.Abs(s.workspaceDir)\n        resolvedWorkspace = filepath.Clean(resolvedWorkspace)\n    }\n    \n    cleanPath := filepath.Clean(p)\n    if filepath.IsAbs(cleanPath) {\n        cleanPath = strings.TrimLeft(cleanPath, string(os.PathSeparator))\n    }\n    \n    fullPathCandidate := filepath.Clean(filepath.Join(resolvedWorkspace, cleanPath))\n    \n    relPath, relErr := filepath.Rel(resolvedWorkspace, fullPathCandidate)\n    if relErr != nil {\n        return \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"access denied\")\n    }\n    \n    if strings.HasPrefix(relPath, \"..\"+string(os.PathSeparator)) || relPath == \"..\" {\n        return \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"access denied\")\n    }\n    \n    resolvedFinalPath, err := filepath.EvalSymlinks(fullPathCandidate)\n    if err == nil {\n        if _, relErr := filepath.Rel(resolvedWorkspace, resolvedFinalPath); relErr != nil {\n            return \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"access denied\")\n        }\n        return resolvedFinalPath, nil\n    }\n    \n    return fullPathCandidate, nil\n}\n```\n\n### 5.8 文件上传 Handler\n\n```go\nfunc (s *Server) UploadFileHandler(c *gin.Context) {\n    contentType := c.ContentType()\n    \n    if strings.HasPrefix(contentType, \"multipart/form-data\") {\n        s.handleMultipartUpload(c)\n    } else {\n        s.handleJSONBase64Upload(c)\n    }\n}\n\nfunc (s *Server) handleJSONBase64Upload(c *gin.Context) {\n    var req UploadFileRequest\n    if err := c.ShouldBindJSON(&req); err != nil {\n        c.JSON(http.StatusBadRequest, gin.H{\"error\": err.Error(), \"code\": 400})\n        return\n    }\n    \n    content, err := base64.StdEncoding.DecodeString(req.Content)\n    if err != nil {\n        c.JSON(http.StatusBadRequest, gin.H{\"error\": \"invalid base64 content\", \"code\": 400})\n        return\n    }\n    \n    safePath, err := s.sanitizePath(req.Path)\n    if err != nil {\n        c.JSON(http.StatusForbidden, gin.H{\"error\": err.Error(), \"code\": 403})\n        return\n    }\n    \n    fileMode := parseFileMode(req.Mode)\n    if err := os.WriteFile(safePath, content, fileMode); err != nil {\n        c.JSON(http.StatusInternalServerError, gin.H{\"error\": err.Error(), \"code\": 500})\n        return\n    }\n    \n    c.JSON(http.StatusOK, FileInfo{\n        Path:     req.Path,\n        Size:     int64(len(content)),\n        Mode:     fmt.Sprintf(\"%o\", fileMode),\n        Modified: time.Now(),\n    })\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 6. 错误处理\n\n### 6.1 错误类型\n\n| 错误场景 | HTTP 状态码 | 错误信息 |\n|----------|-------------|----------|\n| 缺少 Authorization Header | 401 | `missing authorization header` |\n| JWT 格式错误 | 401 | `invalid authorization header format` |\n| JWT 无效/过期 | 401 | `Invalid token` |\n| 请求体超过限制 | 400 | `http: request body too large` |\n| 路径不在 Workspace 内 | 403 | `access denied` |\n| 文件未找到 | 404 | `file not found` |\n| 服务器内部错误 | 500 | 错误描述 |\n\n### 6.2 错误处理策略\n\n- 所有错误返回 JSON 格式 `{\"error\": string, \"code\": int}`\n- 认证错误额外包含 `detail` 字段\n- 路径安全检查失败返回 403，不透露内部路径结构\n- 超时返回 exit code 124（与 `timeout` 命令一致）\n\n---\n\n## 7. 测试策略\n\n### 7.1 单元测试\n\n| 模块 | 测试重点 |\n|------|----------|\n| `AuthManager` | 公钥加载、Token 验证、错误处理 |\n| `ExecuteHandler` | 命令执行、超时处理、环境变量 |\n| `UploadFileHandler` | JSON 上传、Multipart 上传、路径验证 |\n| `ListFilesHandler` | 文件列表、目录遍历 |\n| `DownloadFileHandler` | 文件下载、Content-Type |\n| `sanitizePath` | 路径穿越防御、符号链接处理 |\n\n### 7.2 测试场景\n\n| 场景 | 预期结果 |\n|------|----------|\n| 有效 JWT 请求 | 执行成功，返回结果 |\n| 缺少 JWT | 401 Unauthorized |\n| 无效 JWT | 401 Unauthorized |\n| 命令超时 | exit_code = 124 |\n| 路径穿越尝试 | 403 Forbidden |\n| 文件上传成功 | 返回文件信息 |\n| 不存在的文件下载 | 404 Not Found |\n\n### 7.3 测试覆盖率目标\n\n| 组件 | 目标覆盖率 |\n|------|-----------|\n| auth.go | 90% |\n| execute.go | 90% |\n| files.go | 90% |\n\n---\n\n## 8. 配置\n\n### 8.1 CLI 参数\n\n| Flag | Type | Default | Description |\n|------|------|---------|-------------|\n| `-port` | int | 8080 | PicoD 服务器监听端口 |\n| `-workspace` | string | \"\" | 文件操作根目录（默认为当前工作目录） |\n\n### 8.2 环境变量\n\n| Name | Required | Description |\n|------|----------|-------------|\n| `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` | Yes | PEM 编码的 RSA 公钥 |\n\n---\n\n## 9. 依赖\n\n### 9.1 外部依赖\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|---------|\n| `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` | ^1.9.x | HTTP 框架 |\n| `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` | ^5.0.0 | JWT 验证 |\n| `k8s.io/klog/v2` | ^2.x | 日志 |\n\n### 9.2 内部依赖\n\n| Module | Purpose |\n|--------|---------|\n| 无 | 独立模块，不依赖其他 agentcube 包 |\n\n---\n\n## 10. 参考\n\n- [Code Execution Design](code-execution/design.md)\n- [Deployment client-go](deployment/client-go.md)\n- [sdd_prompt.md](.sdd_prompt.md)","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/picod/design.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/picod/design.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/picod/design.md","time":{"start":1775852808609,"end":1775852808627}}}}
